Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy successfully produced an antidote to help Stacy recover,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but Werewolf smashed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, there was one more drop of the potion left,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so Stacy recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s that you’re sitting in my seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can’t fly the airplane like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll leave right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem a little off, Stacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,once I head back, I’ll be moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I might never get to see Slowy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure you’ll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that I like fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could watch them with Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I spent many nights creating fireworks to surprise Stacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was just too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I didn’t even get to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys better not tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking me home, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some goji tea for you to drink on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the weather’s getting colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to wear more layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, why don’t you eat this cake before leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have many things that I haven’t—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,aren’t you going to say goodbye to Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that if I see him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d be too reluctant to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you exchange contact information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys can still communicate no matter how far apart you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Slowy wants to say goodbye to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowy…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go say goodbye to Slowy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take you back to Goats’ Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If your cover gets blown, things will get complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just taking her back to Goats’ Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With Mr. Slowy acting like that, how can we not worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we were right to follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like everyone is worried about Mr. Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry. We’re here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re almost at Goats’ Village, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, we ran after each other just like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Running after
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,our
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,own
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m even slower than a little kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and what’s more, I’ve sprained my back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t even speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just a bit tired. You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you walk, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No… No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll just lay here for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just hear something snap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that might have been my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy, don’t you think that this cart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is kind of ruining my image?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ride that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot to go to the bus station to say goodbye to Stacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These fireworks will definitely make a great surprise for Stacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The laboratory is right up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowy isn’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You both grow plants on your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a relative of Slowy’s, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That… That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he went to see me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s even on the calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s hurry up and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Stacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m almost there, Stacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could someone help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, I’m late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s mutton pot for dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re not going to be your mutton pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy is here to rescue us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With just a spark, you guys will
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,be done for—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we braise them in soy sauce or steam them in clear soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t even said goodbye to Stacy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We won’t ever get to watch the stars together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,paint together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or plant flowers together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter how touching it can get,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,stomachs still need to be filled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven’t you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This little guy is pretty cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I’m getting bullied!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the ones bullying my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Buffie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you dropped a firework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand is shaking really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I can’t get to the bus station in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go sit down over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been waiting for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you need from Mr. Handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My time is very precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Need something? Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He’ll be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s wait for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re out of time. I have to get on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Slowy and I ever meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the distance, he will keep writing you letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will write back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You two will plan to meet up again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to watch fireworks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You two will make a lot of beautiful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m glad you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I… Am I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You’ve still got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I still didn’t get to see Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Stacy!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
